# NAME

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_changeusername - Change username for the posix account of a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_changeusername *new_username* *old_username*

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to change the username of a user.

# WARNINGS

If the user has also external accounts, theese won't be affected.
Internal accounts, like samba, that depend on the existence of
posix one, will be deleted, but *not recreated*.

# EXAMPLES

	schoolmesh_posixaccount_changeusername johnn john

